{
  "facts": {
    "datasets": [
      "BFCL Non-Live/BFCL V1 single-turn stateless tool calling, with simple, multiple, parallel, parallel_multiple, and irrelevance categories.",
      "BFCL Live/BFCL V2 community-contributed single-turn data; reported for simple, multiple, irrelevance, and relevance suite.",
      "τ2-Bench multi-turn stateful tool-calling across airline, retail, and telecom domains."
