      "WideSearch end-to-end systems: Claude, Gemini, OpenAI o3.",
      "WideSearch multi-agent framework baselines using Claude Sonnet 4, Gemini 2.5 Pro, OpenAI o3-high, Kimi K2, DeepSeek-R1, Doubao-1.6 variants.",
      "XBench baselines include foundation models with tools, deep research systems, and open-source agentic models such as Minimax-M2, DeepSeek-V3.2, GLM-4.5, MiroFlow, Kimi-Researcher, OAgents, DeepMiner-32B-RL, WebShaper-32B, and WebSailor-32B."
