      {
        "claim": "Ablations show learned orchestrator skills have the largest effect: removing them drops WideSearch SR/Row F1/Item F1 from 38.50/63.53/80.12 to 7.00/45.23/62.87 and XBench accuracy from 73.0 to 41.0.",
