        "evidence": "Table 1."
      },
      {
        "claim": "On XBench-DeepSearch, Web2BigTable reports 73.0 accuracy, slightly above Minimax-M2 and MiroFlow at 72.0.",
        "evidence": "Table 4; Figure 6; Section 3.5 XBench-DeepSearch results."
      }
    ]
  },
