        "what_missing": "The review omits the Table 2 comparison against the exact backbone models used inside Web2BigTable.",
        "why_important": "This comparison is the paper's primary attempt to separate framework gains from raw model capability.",
        "evidence": "Table 2: GPT-5 mini single agent 4.00 SR/22.10 Row F1/33.28 Item F1; Gemini 3 Flash single agent 3.00/18.70/31.61; Web2BigTable 38.50/63.53/80.12."
